_sText:
This is a new type of maps that is: Terrorists are ninjas and ct's are the targets. CT's are not allowed to have any gun except USP and Terrorists are only allowed to use a knife, even tho they pick up a gun.  The ninjas are somewhere around them and the point of this is to assassinate the counter-terrorists.
Max T  = 4
Max CT = 16 
This map is still being designed and the floor has now been changed to concrete instead of just plain white. I intend to realease the final version after a few days and then all problems will be sorted.

To get the map into you map folder , u rename the file ti ninja_warehouse.bsp and put it in the C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\<account name>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps


Ps. People got used to jailbreak so this will be just the same.


We are working on a Ninja-Mod and hopefully that will be online soon.

                                           -Ethereal-Cookie-
